      <title>英国央行曼恩：需要更大幅度降息来“消除噪音”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-englands-mann-bigger-rate-cut-was-needed-cut-through-noise-2025-02-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行决策者凯瑟琳·曼恩周二表示，她上周投票支持将利率下调半个百分点，以“消除关于正确政策立场的噪音”，但表示利率需要保持限制性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/bank-englands-mann-bigger-rate-cut-was-needed-cut-through-noise-2025-02-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>专注于气候领域的风险投资公司 Junction Growth Investors 筹集 1.15 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/climate-focused-venture-capital-firm-junction-growth-investors-raises-115-mln-2025-02-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Junction Growth Investors 是一家为应对气候变化的公司提供资金的投资公司，该公司周二表示，已筹集 1.15 亿欧元（1.198 亿美元），凸显出投资者对该领域的热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/climate-focused-venture-capital-firm-junction-growth-investors-raises-115-mln-2025-02-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:10:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国圣公会即将开始整改保护系统</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/church-england-due-begin-overhaul-safeguarding-system-2025-02-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国圣公会将于周二迈出改革其保护体系的第一步，使其独立于宗教机构，寻求在处理虐待问题上几次失败后恢复信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/church-england-due-begin-overhaul-safeguarding-system-2025-02-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
