      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/del-vecchio-family-holding-delfin-considering-selling-unicredit-stake-corriere-2025-02-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《晚邮报》周二援引银行消息人士报道称，德尔维基奥家族控股公司 Delfin 正在探索出售其所持意大利联合信贷银行 2.7% 股份的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/del-vecchio-family-holding-delfin-considering-selling-unicredit-stake-corriere-2025-02-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 06:15:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
